Airbus Confirms Pledge to Guarantee Jobs in Germany Through 2020

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-10-07T08:42:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/airbus-confirms-pledge-to-guarantee-jobs-in-germany-through-2020.html
Airbus SAS confirmed it submitted an
offer to secure jobs in  Germany  until the end of 2020 to the IG
Metall labor union, the company said in an e-mailed statement
today. Airbus added that it cannot comprehend the strike action
announced by the union.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mariajose Vera at 
 mvera1@bloomberg.net  